            "id": 6010325,
            "title": "〈航運指數〉SCFI連5漲 船公司下周可能調漲歐洲線運價",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>上海航交所今 (23) 日公告最新一期上海出口集裝箱運價指數 (SCFI)，較上周再度反彈 167.64 點至 2240.35 點，呈現連 5 漲，四大長程航線運價同步續強，貨攬業者表示，5 月海空運需求均偏強，現處在關稅豁免期，除了美國線強漲，歐洲線也醞釀漲價。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010325%2Fl%2F3bf498c0f683b12416dc5fedc8c92af1.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">SCFI連5漲。(圖：長榮海運提供資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>貨攬業者表示，自 5 月中旬起海運運價連連走升，下周美東線運價已看到 7 字頭，而歐洲目前艙位緊，不排除 6 月中旬過後船公司還會再漲 500 美元。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>本周遠東到美東每 FEU(標準 40 呎貨櫃) 報價較上周飆升 696 美元至 6939 美元，漲幅高達 11%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美西線每 FEU 報價續漲 434 美元，來到 5606 美元，漲幅也達 8.39%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>隨著部分船舶開始從歐洲要調到美國線，歐洲線本周續彈 80 美元，每 TEU(標準 20 呎貨櫃) 來到 1667 美元，漲幅 5%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>地中海線也彈升 241 美元，每 TEU 來到 3302 美元，漲幅 7.87%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6010325",
            "pub_date": "2025-06-06 16:01:38",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
